[Quotes]
victory0= "Sanity... what would I do with a useless thing like that?"
victory1= "Finished? It'll never be finished. A battle isn't like some stupid argument. As long as someone's still breathing, the fight isn't over."
victory2= "Death and pain are just a small price to pay for the enjoyment of battle!"
victory3= "Don't be so stuck-up. Just enjoy this! Killing and being killed. They are just a way to pass time."
victory4= "How about I give you an advantage. Cut me anywhere you want."
victory5= "It isn't even interesting fighting against someone who doesn't have their own goals."
victory6= "Drink Nozarashi"
victory7= "there is nothing i can't cut"
victory8= "Fucking Boring"
